{"tid":2518164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜總:社交平台有責任停散失實內容","createTime":"2021-05-05T23:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T23:45:13.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b142fc59020adcc0264fbe25985b3451eccedad","tid":2518164,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:44:37.000Z","msg":"美國白宮稱拜登相信社交平台有責任停止擴散失實內容<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1589431_1_L_20210506033730.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1589431_1_L_20210506033730.jpg&h=5a621115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮表示，總統拜登相信社交平台有責任停止擴散失實內容。<br />\n<br />\n在社交網站Facebook的監察委員會，支持禁止前總統特朗普使用他的Facebook帳戶，但下令重新檢視，並在六個月內提出合理回應後，白宮發言人普薩基並沒有直接評論，但她表示，拜登認為涉及美國所有人健康及安全，主要平台有責任停止擴散失實內容，特別是涉及新冠病毒疫苗及選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589431-20210506.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589431-20210506.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=e8585bf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589431-20210506.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dbac5f14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589431-20210506.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"fa3bb1ec206f6ff3c4c1107aa747e5518314c28b","tid":2518164,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:45:13.000Z","msg":"左膠極權"}]}